# 🏷 @Autowired Annotation

`@Autowired` tells Spring to inject the required dependency automatically.

Example:

```java id="jlwm8"
@Component
class StudentService {

}

@Component
class StudentController {

    @Autowired
    private StudentService service;

}
```

Spring automatically creates and injects `StudentService`.

---

# 💻 Constructor Injection with @Autowired

In Spring Boot 4.x and modern Spring Boot versions, if there is only one constructor, `@Autowired` is optional.

```java id="jlwm9"
@Component
class StudentController {

    private final StudentService service;

    public StudentController(
            StudentService service) {

        this.service = service;

    }

}
```

