# 📦 Qualifier Annotation

When multiple beans of the same type exist, use `@Qualifier`.

```java id="jlwm17"
@Component
class PetrolEngine {

}

@Component
class DieselEngine {

}

@Component
class Car {

    @Autowired
    @Qualifier("dieselEngine")
    private Engine engine;

}
```

---

# 🏷 @Primary Annotation

Marks a bean as the default choice.

```java id="jlwm18"
@Component
@Primary
class DieselEngine {

}
```

